OL,3,C100-year-old D-Day veteran awarded
OL,4,CFrance's highest military honour
OL,6,FA 100-year-old D-Day veteran who lives
OL,7,Fin Cardiff has received France's
OL,8,Fhighest military honour.
OL,10,FJohn Fiddler was presented with the
OL,11,FLegion D'Honneur at HMS Cambria in
OL,12,FCardiff on Wednesday, in recognition
OL,13,Fof his service during the Second World
OL,14,FWar.
OL,16,FMr Fiddler, who served in the Royal
OL,17,FNavy, was 19 when he delivered tanks
OL,18,Fand troops to the beaches of Normandy
OL,19,Fon D-Day.
