OL,3,C100-year-old D-Day veteran awarded
OL,4,CFrance's highest military honour
OL,6,FDuring the D-Day landings, Mr Fiddler
OL,7,Fworked as a leading supply assistant
OL,8,Fon a tank landing ship, whose role was
OL,9,Fto transport tanks and supplies across
OL,10,Fthe Channel and onto the beaches at
OL,11,FNormandy.
OL,13,FAs well as that he also served on HMS
OL,14,FHolmes, a frigate, which was deployed
OL,15,Fon convoys and anti-submarine patrols
OL,16,Fin the Atlantic, the English Channel
OL,17,Fand the North Sea.
