OL,3,C100-year-old D-Day veteran awarded
OL,4,CFrance's highest military honour
OL,6,FOriginally from Edinburgh, Mr Fiddler
OL,7,Fsettled in Cardiff in 1976, following
OL,8,Fa four-year tour of service as a civil
OL,9,Fservant working for the British Army
OL,10,Fin Germany.
OL,12,FHe was presented with the honour by
OL,13,FHelene Treheux-Duchene, French
OL,14,Fambassador to the UK.
OL,16,FMs Treheux-Duchene said: "It is a
OL,17,Fgreat honour for me to recognise and
OL,18,Fexpress our country's heartfelt
OL,19,Fgratitude to a hero who helped
OL,20,Fliberate France.
