OL,3,C100-year-old D-Day veteran awarded
OL,4,CFrance's highest military honour
OL,6,F"Dad was two days short of his 20th
OL,7,Fbirthday when the ship he was on
OL,8,Fdocked in Milford Haven on 8th of May
OL,9,F1945.
OL,11,F"He would recount that, very
OL,12,Fregrettably, by the time he and his
OL,13,Fshipmates had got onto dry land, the
OL,14,Fpubs had already been drunk dry."
